text: George Norman may refer to: * George Warde Norman (1793–1882), English director of the Bank of England, writer on finance, and Kent cricketer * George Norman (cricketer, born 1890) (1890–1964), English cricketer * George Norman (naturalist) (1823–1882), from Hull * George Norman (pentathlete) (born 1927), British Olympic modern pentathlete * George Wesley Norman (1883–1970), printer and political figure in Saskatchewan
